<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After nickel started spiking on Ma=
rch 7, Tsingshan struggled to meet its margin calls. =E2=80=A6 The LME had =
eventually intervened to halt trading a couple of hours after nickel hit $1=
00,000. It also canceled billions of dollars of transactions, bringing the =
price back to $48,078, where it closed the previous day, in what amounted t=
