online stores, GameStop has experimented with pivots into esports and even =
crypto. The company became the poster child for so-called meme stocks, seei=
ng volatile swings in the share price over the last year that have had litt=
le to do with its business fundamentals.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">Classically the reason to split a stock is to make it more=
